TxnVoidType
The type of transaction being voided.

Values:
ARRefundCreditCard, Bill, BillPaymentCheck, BillPaymentCreditCard, Charge, Check, CreditCardCharge, CreditCardCredit, CreditMemo, Deposit, InventoryAdjustment, Invoice, ItemReceipt, JournalEntry, SalesReceipt, VendorCredit

No default value.

*The inventory adjustment form must be closed in the QuickBooks user interface before you can void an inventory adjustment through the SDK.
